Class Link2

java.lang.Object
  com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractDto
      com.poesys.db.dto.Link2
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDbDto, IObserver, ISubject, java.lang.Comparable<IDbDto>
public class Link2
extends AbstractDto

A test DTO class that serves as the second of three objects that participate in associations. This class supports tests for a many-to-many association and for an n-ary (ternary) association.

Author:
Bob Muller (muller@computer.org)
